data.description: This unique 2 bedroom 1 bathroom cottage is located in the Bradenton Historic River District. There is a large den that can be used as a 3rd bedroom. There is a wood burning fireplace, hardwood floors, crown molding, an updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances and a Solace Air cleaning system that cleans, disinfects, and deodorizes your house 24 hours a day. There is a beautiful backyard oasis with gorgeous tropical landscape, a large deck, a firepit, 2 ponds, and 2 storage sheds. A new metal roof was installed in 2020. No CDD or HOA fees. The house is one block from Lewis Park and Riverview Boulevard. Downtown Bradenton and Warner's Bayou Public Boat Ramp is less than 2 miles away.  Just a short drive to the beaches. Call to schedule your showing today!
